{"tid":2211961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 五大 最令人討厭的Youtuber","createTime":"2020-09-21T12:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T14:33:07.000Z","uid":69083,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15f7b4433c741326f38ef388ab6de1a51c2c3d88","tid":2211961,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"gold\">第五位</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZP8nwy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZP8nwy.jpg&h=809d36e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBrian Cha 榮獲 最令人討厭的Youtuber 第5位簡直係實至名歸<br />\n由佢開班掠水呃人，至到係youtuber廣告瘋狂強姦大眾視覺聽覺<br />\n相信無人會唔同意，呢條神棍聽到佢名，已經憎撚埋佢個姓 <br />\n不過近排佢公開批評777，加上佢都算有少少佬味，呢到就少少扣分<br />\n樣衰 ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閪聲：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無觀眾緣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乞撚人憎：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <strong><span class=\"gold\">第四位</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvhh0n6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxvhh0n6.jpg&h=ed20558d&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n笑波子 呢三隻字已經係小學雞嘅代名詞<br />\n先不論佢係黃定藍，但係把聲真係呢.....閪到<br />\n雖然都知笑波子唔係行咩偶像路線，但拍嘅片真係好造作<br />\n但鑑於都有拍過片屌反送中，加上又愛護小動物，呢到扣咗少少分<br />\n樣衰 ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閪聲：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無觀眾緣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乞撚人憎：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <strong><span class=\"gold\">第三位</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NheTyMV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNheTyMV.jpg&h=45321a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好誤會 ！相信大部分觀眾都會多謝 無用公子 呢幾個月大派花生<br />\n揭發屎家軍，亦都係佢嘅癲瘋之作<br />\n之但係佢私怨上腦，寛己嚴人，how much事件其實真係柒咗<br />\n玫瑰馬戲團前半part解釋牽強，再加上Rose Ma流出事件<br />\n雖然斷定唔到同 無用公子 本人有無直接關係<br />\n但單單睇佢幫中資遊戲賣廣告已經足夠令觀眾乞你憎<br />\n樣衰 ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閪聲：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無觀眾緣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乞撚人憎：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <strong><span class=\"gold\">第二位</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnwR4W2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnwR4W2.jpg&h=c2c091a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信都唔洗多講 ！<br />\n呢條肥仔又分享喜悅，又打狗，又奶共扮黃 ！<br />\n如果唔係識半潛水，神早穩奪 最令人討厭的Youtuber 第一位<br />\n咁究竟邊個係 奪得 最撚乞人憎 Youtuber 第一位呢 ?<br />\n樣衰 ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閪聲：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無觀眾緣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乞撚人憎：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <strong><span class=\"gold\">第一位</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UAwbkwK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAwbkwK.png&h=7ac899ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n恭喜哂 ！伍狗 ！<br />\n呢隻伍狗，youtuber界最撚小氣！Bob叔 大J 係咁意屌咗佢一句<br />\n人地已經有一排避開唔講，但呢隻小氣狗<br />\n幾乎日日出片追擊人，日日搞分化，仲真係以為自己係炒緊娛樂花生 <br />\n學人講佛學，學人講中醫健身，但係佢本人眉心就愈生愈窄，<br />\n小人氣量度他人，youtube d留言屌親佢嘅，都靜靜雞刪哂<br />\ndislike多又屈 無用公子 刷佢數<br />\n俾鍾生凶兩凶，即刻龜縮道歉賴屎<br />\n亦從來無見過佢大大聲追擊藍屍KOL<br />\n最令人討厭的Youtuber 第1位 你當之無愧啦 <br />\n樣衰 ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閪聲：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無觀眾緣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乞撚人憎：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0048f3d0405f6d49f381ef2cbcddb1aafd9b8016","tid":2211961,"uid":69083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"以上內容 純屬真心乞我憎而出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c3b8736b33f48b31374fc67c355ca233a502a2"